---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const effectiveDate = "May 17, 2026";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy · Gerard Agba" description="Privacy policy for agbagerard.com.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-24">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-4">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Effective: {effectiveDate}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert mt-10 max-w-none space-y-6 text-[color:var(--color-fg)] leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">1. What this site is</h2>
      <p>
        agbagerard.com is the personal website of Gerard Agba, a freelance n8n
        workflow builder. It exists to share free workflow templates and offer
        paid services to direct-to-consumer (DTC) brands.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">2. What I collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[color:var(--color-muted)] space-y-2">
        <li><strong class="text-white">Email address</strong> — when you submit a form to download a workflow template or subscribe to the newsletter.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Basic analytics</strong> — anonymous page views, country-level geography, referrer. No fingerprinting.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Booking info</strong> — if you book a call via Cal.com/Calendly, that service collects name, email, and any details you provide.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">3. Where it goes</h2>
      <p>
        Email submissions are stored by <a href="https://beehiiv.com" class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">Beehiiv</a>,
        my email service provider. Booking data is stored by the calendar
        provider (Cal.com or Calendly). Analytics is stored anonymously by
        GitHub Pages access logs and (if added later) a privacy-friendly
        analytics tool. I don&rsquo;t sell or share your data.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">4. How you can opt out or delete your data</h2>
      <p>
        Every newsletter email includes a one-click unsubscribe link.
        To delete your data entirely, email <a href="mailto:hello@agbagerard.com" class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">hello@agbagerard.com</a>
        and I&rsquo;ll remove you from all systems within 14 days (typically 1&ndash;2 days).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site does not set tracking cookies. Embedded videos (YouTube)
        and forms (Beehiiv) may set their own cookies when loaded.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">6. Children</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed to children under 16 and I do not knowingly
        collect data from them.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions: <a href="mailto:hello@agbagerard.com" class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">hello@agbagerard.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
